# apps/backend/src/modules/webhook/

## Responsibility
Inbound WhatsApp webhook verification, payload ingestion, media proxying, and outbound webhook management.

## Design
Elysia route layer backed by a service that handles external payload parsing, queueing, and downstream event dispatch. Verification token is read from env.

## Flow
GET /webhooks/whatsapp verifies Meta challenge, POST /webhooks/whatsapp hands payload to WebhookService, and media routes stream stored media by message id. CRUD routes manage app webhooks.

## Integration
Connects to conversation/message/customer, chatbot, flow runtime, business webhook dispatch, Redis/queue, and S3 media storage.

